CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

April 27, 2006

[Cite as 04/27/2006 Case Announcements, 2006-Ohio-2056.]

*1428MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2006-0202. Tarr v. Williams.

In Habeas Corpus. This cause came on for further consideration of petitioner’s motion for relief from judgment. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion is denied.
